This paper deals with similarity search on time series data, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes a novel hashing scheme that uses sketching and shingling techniques, which are commonly used in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG).
